        <updateDate>2018-08-14T17:57:48Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Pet Emergency Transparency and Accountability in Disasters Act or the PET AID Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act to require a governmental entity that receives assistance under such Act to maintain for a specified period, and make available to the public, records on activities relating to the intake, care, and disposition of animals funded with such assistance.</p> ]]></text>
      </summary>
